8. the thing conceived in the mind  
as one of the three things about which the astrologer is consulted. பார். நஷ்டம் and முஷ்டி. compare சிந்தை. உனக்கொருசிந்தனையுமில்லை. you need have no concern  
2. (r.) there is nothing against you  
எண்ணம்  
